"    - For `source='order_note'`: Use `order_number` to navigate to order "
"detail\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    Eine paginierte Liste von Kundennachrichten aus allen Quellen abrufen.\n"
"\n"
"**Rate Limit:** 300 Anfragen pro Minute\n"
"\n"
"**Quellen:**\n"
"- `contact_form`: Nachrichten aus Kontaktformular-Übergaben\n"
"- `order_note`: Kundennotizen, die an Bestellungen angehängt sind\n"
"\n"
"Nachrichten werden standardmäßig nach neuesten sortiert.\n"
"\n"
"**Deep Linking:**\n"
"- Für `source='contact_form'`: `message_id` verwenden, um zur "
"Nachrichtendetailansicht zu navigieren\n"
"- Für `source='order_note'`: `order_number` verwenden, um zur Bestell-"
"detailansicht zu navigieren\n"
"    "

msgid "Filter by source: 'all', 'contact_form', 'order_note'"
msgstr "Nach Quelle filtern: 'all', 'contact_form', 'order_note'"

msgid "Filter by status: 'all', 'unread', 'read', 'replied', 'archived'"
msgstr ""
"Nach Status filtern: 'all', 'ungelesen', 'gelesen', 'beantwortet', "
"'archiviert'"

msgid "Search by sender name, email, or subject"
msgstr "Nach Absendername, E-Mail oder Betreff suchen"

msgid "Get message details"
msgstr "Nachrichtendetails abrufen"

#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"    Get full details of a customer message.\n"
"\n"
"    **Rate Limit:** 300 requests per minute\n"
"\n"
"    **URL Format:** `/messages/{source}/{id}/`\n"
"    - `source`: Either 'contact_form' or 'order_note'\n"
"    - `id`: The message ID within that source\n"
"\n"
"    Automatically marks the message as read if it was unread.\n"
"\n"
"    **Deep Linking:**\n"
"    - For `source='contact_form'`: Returns full contact form message\n"
"    - For `source='order_note'`: Returns order note with order info for "
"linking\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    Erhalte vollständige Details einer Kundennachricht.\n"
"\n"
"**Rate Limit:** 300 Anfragen pro Minute\n"
"\n"
"**URL-Format:** `/messages/{source}/{id}/`\n"
"- `source`: Entweder 'contact_form' oder 'order_note'\n"
"- `id`: Die Nachrichten-ID innerhalb dieser Quelle\n"
"\n"
"Markiert die Nachricht automatisch als gelesen, wenn sie ungelesen war.\n"
"\n"
"**Deep Linking:**\n"
"- Für `source='contact_form'`: Gibt die vollständige Kontaktformular-"
"Nachricht zurück\n"
"- Für `source='order_note'`: Gibt eine Bestellnotiz mit Bestellinformationen "
"zur Verknüpfung zurück\n"
"    "

msgid "Message not found."
msgstr "Nachricht nicht gefunden."

msgid "Invalid source. Must be \"contact_form\" or \"order_note\"."
msgstr "Ungültige Quelle. Muss \"contact_form\" oder \"order_note\" sein."

msgid "Update message status"
msgstr "Nachrichtenzustand aktualisieren"

#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"    Update the status of a customer message.\n"
"\n"
"    **Rate Limit:** 300 requests per minute\n"
"\n"
"    **URL Format:** `/messages/{source}/{id}/status/`\n"
"    - `source`: Either 'contact_form' or 'order_note'\n"
"    - `id`: The message ID within that source\n"
"\n"
"    **Status Options:**\n"
"    - read: Mark as read\n"
"    - replied: Mark as replied (contact_form only)\n"
"    - archived: Archive the message (contact_form only)\n"
"\n"
"    Note: OrderNotes only support 'read' status.\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    Den Status einer Kundennachricht aktualisieren.\n"
"\n"
"**Rate Limit:** 300 Anfragen pro Minute\n"
"\n"
"**URL Format:** `/messages/{source}/{id}/status/`\n"
"- `source`: Entweder 'contact_form' oder 'order_note'\n"
"- `id`: Die Nachrichten-ID innerhalb dieser Quelle\n"
"\n"
"**Status-Optionen:**\n"
"- read: Als gelesen markieren\n"
"- replied: Als beantwortet markieren (nur bei contact_form)\n"
"- archived: Nachricht archivieren (nur bei contact_form)\n"
"\n"
"Hinweis: OrderNotes unterstützen nur den Status 'read'.\n"
"    "

msgid "Invalid status update."
msgstr "Ungültige Zustandsaktualisierung."

msgid "Order notes only support \"read\" status."
msgstr "Bestellnotizen unterstützen nur den Status \"gelesen\"."

msgid "Message status updated successfully."
msgstr "Nachrichtenzustand erfolgreich aktualisiert."

msgid "Get unread message count"
msgstr "Anzahl ungelesener Nachrichten abrufen"

msgid ""
"\n"
"    Get the count of unread customer messages from all sources.\n"
"\n"
"    **Rate Limit:** 300 requests per minute\n"
"\n"
"    Useful for badge display in the app.\n"
"\n"
"    Returns breakdown by source:\n"
"    - `contact_form`: Unread contact form submissions\n"
"    - `order_note`: Unread customer notes on orders\n"
"    - `total`: Combined total\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    Die Anzahl ungelesener Kundennachrichten aus allen Quellen abrufen.\n"
"\n"
"**Rate Limit:** 300 Anfragen pro Minute\n"
"\n"
"Nützlich für die Anzeige von Badges in der App.\n"
"\n"
"Gibt eine Aufschlüsselung nach Quelle zurück:\n"
"- `contact_form`: ungelesene Kontaktformular-Einreichungen\n"
"- `order_note`: ungelesene Kundennotizen zu Bestellungen\n"
"- `total`: Gesamtsumme\n"
"    "

msgid "Get message counts by status"
msgstr "Nachrichtenzahlen nach Zustand abrufen"

msgid ""
"\n"
"    Get count of messages by status and source for badge display.\n"
"\n"
"    **Rate Limit:** 300 requests per minute\n"
"\n"
"    Returns counts for both sources:\n"
"    - `contact_form`: Full status breakdown (unread, read, replied, "
"archived)\n"
"    - `order_note`: Simple status (unread, read)\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    Zählt Nachrichten nach Status und Quelle für die Anzeige der Badge.\n"
"\n"
"**Rate Limit:** 300 Anfragen pro Minute\n"
"\n"
"Gibt Zahlen für beide Quellen zurück:\n"
"- `contact_form`: Vollständige Statusanalyse (ungelesen, gelesen, "
"beantwortet, archiviert)\n"
"- `order_note`: Einfacher Status (ungelesen, gelesen)\n"
"    "

msgid "Reply to customer message"
msgstr "Auf Kundennachricht antworten"

#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"    Reply to a customer message from the contact form.\n"
"\n"
"    **Rate Limit:** 300 requests per minute\n"
"\n"
"    **URL Format:** `/messages/contact_form/{id}/reply/`\n"
"\n"
"    This endpoint:\n"
"    1. Stores the reply text against the message\n"
"    2. Updates message status to 'replied'\n"
"    3. Optionally sends an email to the customer\n"
"\n"
"    Note: This endpoint only works for `contact_form` messages.\n"
"    For order notes, use the order notes reply endpoint instead.\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    Antwort auf eine Kundennachricht aus dem Kontaktformular.\n"
"\n"
"**Rate Limit:** 300 Anfragen pro Minute\n"
"\n"
"**URL Format:** `/messages/contact_form/{id}/reply/`\n"
"\n"
"Dieser Endpunkt:\n"
"1. Speichert den Antworttext in Verbindung mit der Nachricht\n"
"2. Aktualisiert den Nachrichtenzustand auf 'beantwortet'\n"
"3. Sendet optional eine E-Mail an den Kunden\n"
"\n"
"Hinweis: Dieser Endpunkt funktioniert nur für `contact_form`-Nachrichten.\n"
"Für Bestellnotizen verwenden Sie stattdessen den Endpunkt zur Antwort auf "
"Bestellnotizen.\n"
"    "

msgid "Invalid reply data."
msgstr "Ungültige Antwortdaten."

msgid "List orders"
msgstr "Bestellungen auflisten"

msgid ""
"\n"
"    Get a paginated list of orders with filtering and sorting.\n"
"\n"
"    **Rate Limit:** 300 requests per minute\n"
"\n"
"    **Filtering:**\n"
"    Use either `status` for a specific status or `filter_type` for status "
"groups.\n"
"    If `status` is provided (not 'all'), `filter_type` is ignored.\n"
"\n"
"    **Filter Types (groups):**\n"
"    - all: All orders (default)\n"
"    - open: Orders with status pending or processing\n"
"    - completed: Orders with status shipped or delivered\n"
"    - refunded: Orders with status refunded or cancelled\n"
"\n"
"    **Sort Options:**\n"
"    - -created_at: Newest first (default)\n"
"    - created_at: Oldest first\n"
"    - -total_amount: Highest value first\n"
"    - total_amount: Lowest value first\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    Erhalte eine paginierte Liste von Bestellungen mit Filterung und "
"Sortierung.\n"
"\n"
"**Rate Limit:** 300 Anfragen pro Minute\n"
"\n"
"**Filterung:**\n"
"Verwenden Sie entweder `status` für einen bestimmten Status oder "
"`filter_type` für Gruppen von Status.\n"
"Wenn `status` angegeben wird (nicht 'all'), wird `filter_type` ignoriert.\n"
"\n"
"**Filtertypen (Gruppen):**\n"
"- all: Alle Bestellungen (Standard)\n"
"- open: Bestellungen mit Status 'pending' oder 'processing'\n"
"- completed: Bestellungen mit Status 'shipped' oder 'delivered'\n"
"- refunded: Bestellungen mit Status 'refunded' oder 'cancelled'\n"
"\n"
"**Sortierungsoptionen:**\n"
"- -created_at: Neueste zuerst (Standard)\n"
"- created_at: Älteste zuerst\n"
"- -total_amount: Höchster Wert zuerst\n"
"- total_amount: Niedrigster Wert zuerst\n"
"    "

msgid ""
"Filter type: 'all', 'open', 'completed', 'refunded'. Ignored if 'status' is "
"provided."
msgstr ""
"Filtertyp: 'all', 'open', 'completed', 'refunded'. Wird ignoriert, wenn "
"'status' angegeben ist."

msgid "Specific status filter"
msgstr "Spezifischer Status-Filter"

msgid "Search by order number, email, customer name, or phone number"
msgstr "Nach Bestellnummer, E-Mail, Kundenname oder Telefonnummer suchen"

msgid "Sort field"
msgstr "Sortierfeld"

msgid "Get order details"
msgstr "Bestelldetails abrufen"

msgid ""
"\n"
"    Get full details of a specific order.\n"
"\n"
"    **Rate Limit:** 300 requests per minute\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    Erhalte vollständige Details zu einer bestimmten Bestellung.\n"
"\n"
"**Rate Limit:** 300 Anfragen pro Minute\n"
"    "

msgid "Get order notes"
msgstr "Bestellnotizen abrufen"

msgid ""
"\n"
"    Get all notes for an order (both merchant and customer notes).\n"
"\n"
"    **Rate Limit:** 300 requests per minute\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    Holt alle Notizen zu einer Bestellung (beide Händler- und "
"Kundennotizen).\n"
"\n"
"**Rate Limit:** 300 Anfragen pro Minute\n"
"    "

msgid "Add note to order"
msgstr "Notiz zur Bestellung hinzufügen"

msgid ""
"\n"
"    Add a note to an order. Can be used to reply to customer messages.\n"
"\n"
"    **Rate Limit:** 30 requests per minute (sensitive operation)\n"
"\n"
"    **Fields:**\n"
"    - `note`: The note content (required)\n"
"    - `is_customer_visible`: Whether the customer can see this note "
"(default: true)\n"
"    - `notify_customer`: Whether to send email notification to customer "
"(default: false)\n"
"\n"
"    When replying to a customer's order note, set `is_customer_visible: "
"true` so\n"
"    the customer can see your response in their order history.\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    Eine Notiz zu einer Bestellung hinzufügen. Kann verwendet werden, um auf "
"Nachrichten des Kunden zu antworten.\n"
"\n"
"**Rate Limit:** 30 Anfragen pro Minute (sensible Operation)\n"
"\n"
"**Felder:**\n"
"- `note`: Inhalt der Notiz (erforderlich)\n"
"- `is_customer_visible`: Ob der Kunde diese Notiz sehen kann (Standard: "
"true)\n"
"- `notify_customer`: Ob eine E-Mail-Benachrichtigung an den Kunden gesendet "
"werden soll (Standard: false)\n"
"\n"
"Wenn Sie auf eine Notiz des Kunden antworten, legen Sie "
"`is_customer_visible: true` fest,\n"
"so dass der Kunde Ihre Antwort in seiner Bestellhistorie sehen kann.\n"
"    "

msgid "Invalid note data."
msgstr "Ungültige Notizdaten."

msgid "Note added successfully."
msgstr "Notiz erfolgreich hinzugefügt."

msgid "Update order status"
msgstr "Bestellstatus aktualisieren"

msgid ""
"\n"
"    Update the status of an order.\n"
"\n"
"    **Rate Limit:** 30 requests per minute (sensitive operation)\n"
"\n"
"    **Allowed Transitions:**\n"
"    - pending → processing, cancelled\n"
"    - processing → shipped, cancelled, pending\n"
"    - shipped → delivered, processing\n"
"    - delivered → refunded\n"
"    - cancelled → pending (reopen)\n"
"    - refunded → (terminal state)\n"
"\n"
"    Optionally include tracking number when marking as shipped.\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    Aktualisieren Sie den Status einer Bestellung.\n"
"\n"
"**Rate Limit:** 30 Anfragen pro Minute (sensible Operation)\n"
"\n"
"**Erlaubte Übergänge:**\n"
"- pending → processing, cancelled\n"
"- processing → shipped, cancelled, pending\n"
"- shipped → delivered, processing\n"
"- delivered → refunded\n"
"- cancelled → pending (wieder öffnen)\n"
"- refunded → (endgültiger Zustand)\n"
"\n"
"Bei der Kennzeichnung als versendet können Sie optional eine Tracking-Nummer "
"einbeziehen.\n"
"    "

msgid "Order status updated successfully."
msgstr "Bestellstatus erfolgreich aktualisiert."

msgid "Update tracking number"
msgstr "Versandnummer aktualisieren"

msgid ""
"\n"
"    Update or add tracking number for an order.\n"
"\n"
"    **Rate Limit:** 30 requests per minute (sensitive operation)\n"
"    "
